ImplementedSecurityControls.AccessControl: No owner or role-based access control as any user can participate by paying 1 ether.
ImplementedSecurityControls.EtherRequirement: 1 ether entry fee acts as a basic control against spam or unnecessary guesses.

FallbackFunctionality: There is no fallback function in this contract, so it does not accept ether directly outside the intended function calls.
